    "# 02 Topic Modeling\n",
    "\n",
    "## What this stage does\n",
    "Performs Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) using Gensim to extract topics from restaurant reviews. Applies NLTK for stopword removal and lemmatization on a 300K representative sample, before applying the model to the broader dataset.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Input tables/files required\n",
    "- `merged_philly` (Temp View)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Output tables/files produced\n",
    "- `lda_topic_results` (Table)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Key parameters to configure\n",
    "- `NUM_TOPICS`: 25\n",
    "- `SAMPLE_SIZE`: 300,000\n",
    "\n",
    "## Expected runtime\n",
    "- ~45-60 minutes depending on cluster configuration."
   ]
